## 🛠️ Usage in Code
- **FFmpeg**: Use `-rtsp_transport tcp` to avoid packet drop.
- **OpenCV**: `cv2.VideoCapture(url, cv2.CAP_FFMPEG)`
- **Latency**: Expect 500ms-2s latency on RTSP.

## ⚠️ Troubleshooting
- **Black Screen**: Check if `ffplay` works locally. H.265 requires modern decoders.
- **Connection Refused**: Verify VPN/Tailscale. RG NVR needs subnet routing from `rg1/rg2/rg3`.
